VIM HANDBOOK -*- mode:org -*-
The vim handbook

* Navigation

left h
down j
up k
right l

* Deletion
Word deletion: place cursor the the beginning of the word
and  type dw


Move to beginning of sentence 0

Delete a whole line  dd

Replace character: go with the cursor to tht characher , 
type r nd then type character you want

* Undo, Redo, Save Exit
:w write
:wq write and quit
:q! quit and dont save

:u undo
Ctrl + R redo
* Cut,Copy,Paste
PASTE
i) place cursor at begin
ii) V for lines
iii) y
iv) p to paste after cursor

* Search

SEARCH case insensitive
:set ignore case
/your_word and then Enter
n for next occurence N for previous

* Splits and navigation
Move between tabs
Ctrl + w ,w


///
#########################
-----------------------
* Find,replace
Find foo and replace with bar whole words and ask for confirmation

:/s/\<foo\>/bar/gc


Commenting :tim pop
vgc  
v for visual mode

* Plugins

To start using PHP auto completion, press the Ctrl + x followed
 by Ctrl + o keys while writing some PHP functions.
:set omnifunc=phpcomplete#CompletePHP

vim with no plugins 
git remote add origin https://github.com/MrRisoni/vimmie.git

* Git diff

vim diff for merge
nagivate to chanes ]c  and [c
merge :diffput , :difffget
